            "sections": [
                {
                    "body": "Vishkanyas are skilled with poison and never accidentally poison themselves when using or applying poison.", 
                    "name": "Poison Use", 
                    "url": "pfsrd://Bestiary 3/Monsters/Vishkanya/Special Abilities/Poison Use", 
                    "ability_types": {
                        "ability_type_id": 612, 
                        "section_id": 2230, 
                        "ability_type": "Extraordinary"
                    }, 
                    "section_id": 2230, 
                    "source": "Bestiary 3", 
                    "type": "ability"
                }, 
                {
                    "body": "A number of times per day equal to its Constitution modifier (minimum 1/day), a vishkanya can envenom a weapon that it wields with its toxic saliva or blood (using blood requires the vishkanya to be injured when it uses this ability). Applying venom in this way is a swift action.", 
